Code preview of 小额贷项目信息主表sl_smallloan_project

drop table if exists sl_smallloan_project;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: sl_smallloan_project */
/*==============================================================*/
create table sl_smallloan_project
(
projectId bigint(20) not null auto_increment,
operationType smallint(6) not null default 0 comment '业务品种',
flowType smallint(6) not null default 0 comment '流程类别',
mineType smallint(6) not null default 0 comment '我方主体类型',
mineId bigint(20) not null default 0 comment '我方主体表id',
oppositeType smallint(6) not null default 0 comment '对方主体类型',
oppositeID bigint(20) not null default 0 comment '对方主体类型ID(客户表ID)',
projectName varchar(250) not null comment '项目名称',
projectNumber varchar(50) not null comment '项目编号',
projectMoney numeric(10,2) comment '贷款/融资金额',
loanType smallint(6) default 0 comment '担保方式',
dateMode smallint(6) default 0 comment '日期模型',
startDate datetime comment '贷款起始日',
intentDate datetime comment '预计还款日',
accrualtype smallint(6) comment '计息方式',
accrual numeric(10,2) comment '利息',
payaccrualType smallint(6) default 0 comment '付息方式',
payaccrualDate datetime comment '预计付息日',
overdueRate numeric(10,2) comment '逾期费率',
isAheadPay smallint(6) default 0 comment '是否提前还款',
aheadDayNum smallint(6) default 0 comment '提前天数',
breachRate numeric(10,2) default 0.00 comment '违约金比例',
breachMoney numeric(10,2) default 0.00 comment '违约金额',
commisionMoney numeric(10,2) default 0.00 comment '佣金金额',
commisionType smallint(6) default 0 comment '佣金方式',
commitDate datetime comment '项目上报时间',
projectStatus smallint(6) comment '融资项目项目状态(0为贷前项目；1为贷中项目；2为已完成项目；3为提前终止项目)',
accrualMoney numeric(10,2) comment '利息(金额)',
payProjectMoney numeric(10,2) comment '已还金额（本金）',
payAccrualMoney numeric(10,2) comment '已还金额(利息)',
flatMoney numeric(10,2) comment '平帐金额',
annualNetProfit numeric(10,2) comment '年化净利率',
elseMoney numeric(10,2) comment '其它费用',
managerUser bigint(20) comment '用户表id号',
primary key (projectId)
);

alter table sl_smallloan_project comment '小额贷项目信息主表';
